Benjamin Mosha starred for the Dockers as he grabbed a brace, with Abdallah Hassan, Danson Chetambe and Darius Msagha netting the other goals. Hosts Bandari were in ruthless form Tuesday as they thrashed Vihiga United 5-0 in their Football Kenya Federation Premier League match at the Mbaraki grounds, Mombasa. 

Benjamin Mosha starred for the Dockers as he grabbed a brace, with Abdallah Hassan, Danson Chetambe and Darius Msagha netting the other goals. 



